/**
    @page solitaire Solitaire Module

    @section solitaire_overview Overview

    Classic Klondike Solitaire implemented in C with raylib.

    Features:
    - Standard Klondike rules (draw 1 from stock)
    - Card drag-and-drop
    - Auto-complete detection (win condition)
    - Sound effects on card moves
    - Returns to lobby via ESC

    @section solitaire_api Public API

    @ref solitaire_initGame__full — allocate and initialize a game instance  
    @ref solitaire_gameLoop — run one frame (update + render)  
    @ref solitaire_freeGame — free resources and set pointer to NULL  
    @ref solitaire_isRunning — check if the game is still active

    @section solitaire_assets Assets

    Card images are in `jeux/solitaire/assets/solitaire/`:
    - `playingCards.png` — full 52-card sprite sheet
    - `cardBack_blue3.png` — card back texture

    Sound in `jeux/solitaire/assets/sounds/`:
    - `solitaire_cardTurn.wav`
*/
